00:03:58,378 --> 00:04:01,278
"Inubushi Castle, The Ablazed Demon Dog"

44
00:04:01,278 --> 00:04:04,278
"(Footprints Chapter)"

45
00:04:06,578 --> 00:04:07,778
He's cute.

46
00:04:07,778 --> 00:04:12,178
Yes! It would be nice if the demon dog is this way too.

47
00:04:18,978 --> 00:04:20,778
What's the matter?

48
00:04:23,778 --> 00:04:27,278
What's that? Isn't something glowing over there?

49
00:04:27,278 --> 00:04:28,478
Yes.

50
00:04:49,478 --> 00:04:51,178
Kazuha!

51
00:04:54,878 --> 00:04:57,378
Stand up! The front door's right there!

52
00:05:05,478 --> 00:05:08,478
What's all the fuss about?

53
00:05:08,478 --> 00:05:09,978
The demon dog!

54
00:05:09,978 --> 00:05:12,278
The demon dog appeared in the yard!

55
00:05:12,278 --> 00:05:15,178
-Demon dog? -Don't be ridiculous!

56
00:05:15,178 --> 00:05:17,578
It would never appear inside the premises of the house!

57
00:05:17,578 --> 00:05:21,278
Don't tell me it jumped over the fence and came inside.

58
00:05:21,278 --> 00:05:24,078
That's ridiculous.

59
00:05:24,078 --> 00:05:26,678
At any rate, it's dangerous,

60
00:05:26,678 --> 00:05:29,678
so I think that you should stay inside for a while.

61
