What?

205
00:13:54,033 --> 00:13:56,233
-Don't move! -Stay still!

206
00:13:56,233 --> 00:13:58,533
Are you all right?

207
00:13:58,533 --> 00:14:00,333
He was just a little burned, that's all.

208
00:14:00,333 --> 00:14:04,333
By the way, what we just saw...

209
00:14:04,333 --> 00:14:07,233
Demon dog, wasn't it?

210
00:14:07,233 --> 00:14:09,633
What? It came out again?

211
00:14:09,633 --> 00:14:12,033
The demon dog appeared again?

212
00:14:12,033 --> 00:14:15,633
Yeah. It's already the third time tonight.

213
00:14:15,633 --> 00:14:18,433
Was the dog really on fire?

214
00:14:18,433 --> 00:14:20,833
Isn't it some kind of a trick?

215
00:14:20,833 --> 00:14:23,633
Yeah. We thought so too.

216
00:14:23,633 --> 00:14:25,733
But no matter how you look at it...

217
00:14:25,733 --> 00:14:28,733
I think it was really burning!

218
00:14:28,733 --> 00:14:32,033
